desc_long							评测						“. . .it's a deceptively intense experience.”N/A – Joystiq												关于这款游戏							ABOUT THE GAMETHE STORY:Bob and his best friend, Buddy, have travelled the biomes of Highworld using the mighty Realmgates. But when a huge explosion throws Highworld into chaos and separates Bob from his one true love, Starbrite, the blue little Orbite is given incredible power from above and sets out on a quest to bring justice to the evil demons plaguing his world.GAMEPLAY:Super Mega Bob is a 2D SHMUP (shoot-em-up) filled with super intense bullet-dodging, awesome pixel art, insane level design, and epic boss battles. If you're looking for something that will challenge your retro gaming reflexes while providing you with a beautifully nostalgic gaming environment, Super Mega Bob is your kind of game.FEATURES:    160 levels    10 bosses    200+ upgrades    5 biomes    Original 8-bit soundtrack    Beautiful pixel art    Real-time lighting    400 different hat and costume combinationsSUPPORTED RESOLUTIONS: 1024x768, 800x600TRY THE DEMO!Please don't buy a game you're not certain you like - try the demo! The full game adds many more features, but the demo will give you a good idea of whether or not Super Mega Bob is something you'll enjoy.DOWNLOAD DEMO: http://jenito.com/super-mega-bob/smb-download						
